This could be about the new year, but the things I want, I want at any time so I guess the New Year's thing doesn't really count. Usually I prefer "I would like" to "I want" but..oh well. I want: To travel (wherever) To travel (wherever) with someone To stay in a hotel and do hotel-y things just for fun My arm and other bits to be fixed so I don't hurt or struggle anymore To feel important, not just be told I am To actually have the ability to feel important enough to warrant writing out anything else that I want You, to want me.
Should I let the cat 'clean' the dishes? Y/N
Will someone come and spend New Year's with me?

What would make me happy again and perhaps look forward to Christmas like I used to? I dunno, a miracle, something that restores my faith in others, a leap of faith maybe? I'm not saying I need to leap, I've jumped far enough already. I want someone else to put their faith in me for a change, and believe me. Or at least I need to be able to feel it.

They want to take them away because I'm tired and rundown Fuck you I'll try spending as much bonus payment on private psych as I can, and if you think that's anything to do with bludging then I suggest you go put yourself under the duress I am under and just keep going because you have to (ie GET FUCKED as I certainly feel I am that way right now).

I wonder if anyone would bother letting me know, or why wouldnt they
good reason for my disaffection
It'd be nice to be invited to things, even though I most likely wouldn't be able to go (lucky you! Who'd want someone with no prospects like me around anyway?)
I'm not a monster you know, I'm not supposed to be an outcast
if you dont like that then fuck off
A few days ago I purchased Interstella 5555 and watched it today (but not for first time). Whyyyy does it always cause me to tear up? ;_;
If only you would make your mind up..and tell me.

Because it took so long between my doctors appt for MRI results and such (today) and my EMG test (3 1/2 years ago), they have to do another EMG. That is, ELECTROCUTE ME. Not farm-fence-shenannigans electrocute, but torture-grade shenannigans electrocute. I still remember the last time - painful and extremely distressing, that they didnt even get to the second part of the test where they would stick needles into my arm and electrocute me that way. Ugh.. :( PS the MRI results were clear. Woo-bloody-hoo.... PPS I now have another 3 months to wait.

Will anyone lend me a bbq for christmas day/nye, just in case you arent gonna use it yourselves? :P

PS how on earth could a Sound of Music soundtrack CD still be $17, and a Gilbert and Sullivan CD only $7?!?! :O
My dad keeps giving me bottles of wine. I think he's trying to civilize me :S
BTW if you ever wanted to make industrial doofdoof music, inside an MRI machine is the answer (so are the industrial headphones I had to wear).
Thanks Nick, for letting your ears be tortured haha

For my own good I guess.
Sometimes I can't stand watching things happen and not knowing how or being able to do anything about it, and it's the only way I seem to be able to communicate that.
I get so afraid and I've got nowhere else to run to except there.
You'll forget soon enough, won't you?
I am tired.

If that's how it's going to turn out..again, then you know what I'll have to do..again.


And no Mackys, I'm not doing that. Twit.

Everytime I read stuff like I just did, I wonder if 'it's just me'. Obviously I err on the side of 'no' and then I keep asking myself why I continue to hold on. I don't know. I hate the life my brain has made me exist in.
I can't believe that dad asked me yesterday why I was so tired..
Please don't let me run away this time

And so they want to put her on Clonidine during the weekdays starting tomorrow. She's worried, not outwardly so, but I know she is. Almost as scared as I am. What am I doing.. I could do with a visitor or something tomorrow..please?
If anything ever happens to me and I can't be around, I want only my dad to have them. He's the only family I really have.
I wonder if I keep repeating myself, will someone finally hear me?
I wish someone was here right now..

I hate you, Samuel Barber's Adagio for Strings for ALWAYS making me shed a tear everytime I listen to you (whilst reading a report about how a father got his 20 year sentence for repeatedly raping his own daughter reduced to 12 years as the appeal stated it was 'excesive').
What would be a good alternative to drinking myself sane right now? Anyone? ..meh, thought as much.

Okk, at Carousel today I was looking at the Dell display in the mall, and I was commenting on what I thought the game that was playing on the screen was. Me and one of the staff members were talking games, and he was all crysis/COD4 and I was all TF2, and I also said couldnt afford COD4 anyways, its like 70+ bucks even on steam..and then he said the funniest thing EVAR: "well I'm asian, I get everything pirated anyway"
..
I guffawed all the way down the mall
bwahahahaha

I don't think I will be able to sleep tonight, despite me falling asleep at kb now. In fact I haven't slept after going to bed for a long time. I lay there and everything rolls over and over in my head. Everything is failing and I can't find any comfort.

Will someone please buy me a new fridge as an early Christmas present? :(
P.S. Everyone boycott Samsung, and never call DACAPS for repairs *hrmf* :<
I was searching for DIY helium kits for balloons, and the first search result is a page about ExitNet and DIY Helium tools/conversions :S Gawd... or not.
From my last post which got 4 comments, I only got one email notification O_o
Should I have a very belated housewarming (moved in mid October 2007 :P), Y/N?
Nothing like the Anvil Chorus from Il Travatore to get you going after only 3 1/2 hour's sleep -_-
So I'm still here, still desperately need rest/friends/human interaction/a life.. meh who cares? I'm just a drop in the ocean..
